OL,3,CQuadruple killer jailed for life after
OL,4,Cmurdering girlfriend and three
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FA man has been jailed after he
OL,8,Flaunched a fatal knife attack on his
OL,9,Fgirlfriend and her family in a drug
OL,10,Fand alcohol-fuelled rage.
OL,12,FJoshua Jacques, 29, was sentenced to
OL,13,Flife with a minimum term of 46 years
OL,14,Fin prison after he killed Samantha
OL,15,FDrummonds, her mother Tanysha Ofori-
OL,16,FAkuffo, her grandmother Dolet Hill,
OL,17,Fand Ms Hill's partner, Denton Burke at
OL,18,FMs Hill's home in Bermondsey, in April
OL,19,F2022.
