OL,7,FMetropolitan Police officers were
OL,8,Fcalled to a terraced house in Delaford
OL,9,FRoad where the four were found.
OL,11,FJacques left a "bloodbath" in his wake
OL,12,Fwhen he attacked the victims with a
OL,13,Fknife, with officers finding Mr
OL,14,FBurke's body at the foot of the stairs
OL,15,Fand the three women "heaped together"
OL,16,Fin the kitchen.
