OL,7,FArmed police found Jacques naked and
OL,8,Flying in the upstairs bathroom in a
OL,9,Fpraying position, screaming "Allah,
OL,10,Ftake me!", "Kill me now", "Get rid of
OL,11,Fme", and "God please forgive me".
OL,13,FLater, at Lewisham Hospital, Jacques
OL,14,Fsaid: "I ain't even in the wrong, I
OL,15,Fdid them for sacrifice", and also
OL,16,Fwarned: "I will do something stupid
OL,17,Fagain."
OL,19,FHe had admitted their manslaughters
OL,20,Fbut denied murder on the basis that he
OL,21,Fwas mentally unwell at the time.
