OL,7,FAn Old Bailey jury deliberated for two
OL,8,Fhours to find Jacques, from Minard
OL,9,FRoad, Lewisham, south-east London,
OL,10,Fguilty of four counts of murder.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside court at the time of
OL,13,Fthe guilty verdict, relatives of the
OL,14,Fvictims said a whole life sentence was
OL,15,F"only fair" as they condemned Jacques
OL,16,Ffor his lack of remorse.
