OL,7,FTracey-Ann Henry, the aunt of Miss
OL,8,FDrummonds, sister of Ms Ofori-Akuffo
OL,9,Fand Ms Hill, said: "Justice. Justice
OL,10,Fhas been served for my mum, sister,
OL,11,Fniece and stepdad. So, rest in peace.
OL,12,FFinally. Finally."
OL,14,FShe added: "It's affected me really
OL,15,Fbad because I lost my mum, sister,
OL,16,Fniece and stepdad.
OL,18,F"I'm spending my second Christmas
OL,19,Fwithout my family. So, that is very
OL,20,Fgoing to be very emotional on
OL,21,FChristmas Day."
