OL,7,FMr Burke's niece Chyloe Daley said the
OL,8,Fguilty verdict was a "very long time
OL,9,Fcoming".
OL,11,FShe said: "Just the first word that
OL,12,Fcomes is grateful. Sadness, but filled
OL,13,Fwith joy because important things and
OL,14,Fpeople and lives were taken from us
OL,15,Fand, today, we heard what we felt like
OL,16,Fwe've waited over a year for."
OL,18,FShe said the family would "hope and
OL,19,Fpray" that Jacques spends the rest of
OL,20,Fhis life in prison.
