OL,7,FMs Daley added: "It's up to the judge
OL,8,Fat the end of the day. But four family
OL,9,Fmembers were taken and I just think it
OL,10,Fis the only thing we can ask for now.
OL,12,F"I think it's at that level of
OL,13,Fseriousness. Yeah, it's only fair."
OL,15,FOn their lost loved ones, Ms Daley
OL,16,Fadded: "They weren't just lives that
OL,17,Fwere taken, but they were people and
OL,18,Fthey lived and they were funny, and
