OL,7,FIn February 2020, he was jailed for 51
OL,8,Fmonths for conspiring to deal heroin
OL,9,Fand crack cocaine, and possessing
OL,10,Fcannabis. He was released on November
OL,11,F11 2021.
OL,13,FIn probation reports from April last
OL,14,Fyear, Jacques was described as chatty
OL,15,Fand engaged.
OL,17,FThree days before the killing, he
OL,18,Fcalled his probation officer to say
OL,19,Fthat he had been offered a job at a
OL,20,Fradio station.
