OL,7,FTwo days later, Ms Drummonds confided
OL,8,Fin a friend that she believed Jacques
OL,9,Fwas having an "episode" and had been
OL,10,F"chatting all night and was fixated on
OL,11,Ftopics".
OL,13,FMr Little told jurors no medical calls
OL,14,Fwere made before the killings nor was
OL,15,FJacques taken to hospital.
OL,17,FOn April 25, 2022, Jacques visited the
OL,18,Fhouse where Mr Burke and Ms Hill lived
OL,19,Fonly for the second time.
