OL,7,FMs Ofori-Akuffo, also known as
OL,8,FRacquel, sometimes stayed at the
OL,9,Fproperty to care for her mother, who
OL,10,Fwas receiving treatment for cancer,
OL,11,Fwhile Ms Drummonds had been living
OL,12,Fthere as her own flat was undergoing
OL,13,Frenovation, Mr Little told jurors.
OL,15,FAfter Jacques launched his attack, Ms
OL,16,FDrummonds called his mother Norma
OL,17,FDerrivere but all she was able to say
OL,18,Fwas "Norma he's sta... sta... ahhh".
