OL,12,Ffrom his birthday on April 19 last
OL,13,Fyear ` just days before the killings.
OL,15,FHowever, that escalation came weeks
OL,16,Fafter he began having trouble sleeping
OL,17,Fwhich was a symptom of mania, the
OL,18,Fdefence argued.
